    correct: 0,
    explanation: `At $\\theta = 45^\\circ$, $\\sin 2\\theta = \\sin 90^\\circ = 1$, so $R_{\\text{max}} = \\frac{v_0^2 \\times 1}{g} = \\frac{v_0^2}{g}$.`
