    explanation: `Full plank (thickness $d$): $200^2 = 400^2 + 2ad \\rightarrow 2ad = -120000$.\nHalf plank ($d/2$): $v^2 = 400^2 + 2a(d/2) = 160000 - 60000 = 100000$.\n$v = \\sqrt{100000} \\approx 316 \\text{ m/s}$.`
