    q: `Two masses ($5 \\text{ kg}$ on top, $3 \\text{ kg}$ hanging below) are suspended vertically by massless strings and accelerate upward at $2 \\text{ m/s}^2$. Find the tension $T_2$ in the lower string that supports only the $3 \\text{ kg}$ mass.`,
